de.hshl.obj.wavefront.mtl

Class MTLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hshl.obj.wavefront.mtl.MTLParser

  • public final class MTLParser
extends java.lang.Object
    The MTLParser collects predefined line parsers, which specify how each wavefront keyword should be interpreted.

    For example, the keyword "#" indicates that the rest of the line is a comment and should be ignored. On the other hand, the "Kd" keyword declares the diffuse color of a material.
